            <p class="lead">Huntsville is the gateway to Algonquin Park and one of Muskoka's most popular cottage destinations. Summer weekends see thousands of visitors, and the demand for short-term rentals is strong year-round.</p>
            <p class="lead">The Town implemented comprehensive STR regulations through By-law 2025-19, with a focus on protecting neighborhood character and preserving long-term housing. It includes some unique requirements like a 12-month ownership period before licensing. Here's the complete breakdown.</p>
