          <ul>
            <li><strong>Be reachable 24/7</strong> during any guest stay</li>
            <li><strong>Respond to contact</strong> within 30 minutes</li>
            <li><strong>Arrive on-site</strong> within 60 minutes if needed</li>
            <li><strong>Handle noise complaints</strong> and other issues</li>
            <li><strong>Liaise with Town officials</strong> and neighbors</li>
          </ul>

